WEBVTT

00:00.873 --> 00:02.771
<i>Previously on The Borgias...</i>

00:02.872 --> 00:05.573
You will choose a bride in Spain

00:05.640 --> 00:07.638
<i>and you will become the Borgia</i>

00:07.705 --> 00:10.609
<i>I always hoped you would be.</i>

00:10.677 --> 00:14.484
I propose we use the weapon
the Borgia family uses.

00:14.551 --> 00:15.687
Canterella.

00:15.788 --> 00:17.989
Too much and it will kill you.

00:18.057 --> 00:20.328
Just enough, and it
will make you strong.

00:22.100 --> 00:25.371
Dedicate yourself to
the renewal of Christendom.

00:25.439 --> 00:28.909
To the destruction of
the red whore of Rome!

00:28.976 --> 00:30.545
<i>There is a new</i>
<i>order in Florence.</i>

00:30.613 --> 00:32.613
Savonarola virtually
controls the city.

00:32.682 --> 00:34.251
He must be silenced.

00:34.319 --> 00:37.219
We would have Catherina
Sforza come to Rome

00:37.287 --> 00:39.387
and kneel at our feet.

00:39.455 --> 00:41.055
The pope would
request your presence

00:41.156 --> 00:42.490
at the chair of St. Peter's.

00:42.558 --> 00:44.424
Whom does your mother
bow to, my son?

00:44.492 --> 00:45.626
Nobody.

00:45.727 --> 00:47.160
You refuse to come to Rome?

00:47.228 --> 00:48.895
<i>She shared her bed with me.</i>

00:48.962 --> 00:50.763
Did she beg to be
friends with us?

00:50.831 --> 00:52.566
No, she remains an enemy.

00:52.634 --> 00:54.170
Release me from my
cardinal's robes,

00:54.238 --> 00:55.638
give me the papal army,

00:55.706 --> 00:57.441
and I will bring you
Catherina Sforza in chains!

00:57.508 --> 00:59.811
I will not marry.

00:59.878 --> 01:01.379
Never again.

01:01.447 --> 01:03.617
It is a daughter's duty to
marry her father's choice!

01:03.684 --> 01:05.953
So I am to have no
voice in the matter!

01:06.021 --> 01:08.956
Like me, you have
just declared a war.

01:09.024 --> 01:10.426
<i>Which one is the suitor?</i>

01:10.493 --> 01:12.261
<i>Calvino Pallavicini</i>
<i>from Genova.</i>

01:12.362 --> 01:14.263
And, behind him,
in the brown and grey.

01:14.364 --> 01:15.732
Who is he?

01:15.799 --> 01:17.968
<i>His brother, Raffaello.</i>

01:18.036 --> 01:20.905
Your brother's coming home
with a party of conquistadors.

01:21.006 --> 01:22.508
You must embrace him for me-

01:22.576 --> 01:25.878
while I attend to the
Church's business-

01:25.946 --> 01:27.548
back in Florence.

01:32.843 --> 01:34.843
[♪]

